<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GND Propeller Lab</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0f1c, #121a2b);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .background-grid {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #9fb3d8;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .cards {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card {
            width: 320px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: rgba(0,180,255,0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,180,255,0.15);
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #b7c5de;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: #6f86b0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .card {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 360px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="background-grid"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>GND PROPELLER LAB</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">
            FPV Propeller Design & Analysis Toolkit
        </div>

        <div class="cards">
            <a href="propeller_design.html" class="card">
                <div class="icon">🛠️</div>
                <h2>Propeller Design</h2>
                <p>
                    Create and develop a propeller from scratch. 
                    Define geometry, airfoil sections, pitch distribution and aerodynamic parameters.
                </p>
            </a>

            <a href="propeller_analisi.html" class="card">
                <div class="icon">📈</div>
                <h2>Propeller Analysis</h2>
                <p>
                    Analyze existing propellers, compare aerodynamic performance, 
                    inspect geometry and evaluate efficiency.
                </p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            GND LAB • FPV Engineering Tools
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
